# Release History

## 1.3.0 (12-12-2023)
+ Support local schema reference in another referred swagger file

## 1.2.0 (11-29-2023)
+ Added API version as PackageVersion in code file.

## 1.1.0 (6-26-2023)
+ Disabled flatteneing of nested model.
+ Updated definitions to include models all referenced models
+ Included definations referenced in external files
+ Ensure enum values are parsed
+ Ensure all inline schema is parsed
+ Handle allOf an additional Properties
+ Ensure definiton Properties are sorted

## 1.0.9 (5-22-2023)
+ Support schema for parameters referenced in relative files

## 1.0.8 (3-1-2023)

+ Skip any invalid swagger file path when generating API review

## 1.0.7 (2-9-2023)

+ Support header parameter in operation parameters
+ Support header response in operation responses
+ For schemaCache, use absolute path as key

## 1.0.6 (2-2-2023)

+ Remove APIView and APIViewWeb dependency 
+ Fix don't resolve response issue
+ Add null check for array item

## 1.0.5 (1-18-2023)

+ Fix root schema circular reference issue by adding root schema ref in refChain.

## 1.0.4 (11-28-2022)

+ Fix expand array reference issues in definition section. Do not expand array reference in definitions.
+ To keep APIView revision consistent. Json serialization use alwaysMultiline option.
+ Remove unused code and comments.


## 1.0.3 (11-17-2022)

+ Remove trailing colon from API path
+ Support operation level parameters
+ Fix circular reference issue for cross file reference schema


## Version 1.0.2 (11-8-2022)
+ Add null check when cannot resolve reference from schema cache.
+ Change enum type to JsonElement to support different enum type like, string, boolean, int

## Version 1.0.1 (10-31-2022)

+ Fix missing first property for definition
+ Fix wrong "required" property in xMsParameterizedHost parameters by resolving parameter reference
+ Show enum type for definition
+ Support resolve definition files from common types file.

## Version 1.0.0 (10-5-2022)
Initial release.